- Import Plus Jakarta Sans, not system fonts

## AI Stack (Sprint 2+)
- Model: Gemma 4 26B A4B (via Gemini API) for coach + quiz
- Model: Gemma 4 E4B for tutorial summarization
- API: api.google.dev (Gemini API endpoint)
- Key: stored in Firebase Cloud Functions environment (never in frontend)
- All AI calls: routed through Cloud Functions (never direct from frontend)
